31
00:01:14,430 --> 00:01:16,680
Our goal is really to solve important

32
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:18,900
and challenging biological questions,

33
00:01:18,900 --> 00:01:22,830
and so this is very hard
to do in a more traditional

34
00:01:22,830 --> 00:01:24,360
and pure discipline.

35
00:01:24,360 --> 00:01:27,540
Traditionally, people use
dyes and fluorescent proteins

36
00:01:27,540 --> 00:01:29,640
to look at individual molecules,

37
00:01:29,640 --> 00:01:33,180
but these kinds of probes
bleach within tens of seconds,

38
00:01:33,180 --> 00:01:36,390
so we can't look at processes
much longer than that.

39
00:01:36,390 --> 00:01:37,770
With our photostable probe,

40
00:01:37,770 --> 00:01:40,680
we can really visualize with great spatial

41
00:01:40,680 --> 00:01:43,380
and temporal resolutions, great detail.

42
00:01:43,380 --> 00:01:45,810
And so whenever you have a new technology

43
00:01:45,810 --> 00:01:48,450
that can allow you to image faster

44
00:01:48,450 --> 00:01:50,010
with higher spatial resolution

45
00:01:50,010 --> 00:01:52,050
and with longer periods of time,

46
00:01:52,050 --> 00:01:53,730
you are bound to see something new.

47
00:01:53,730 --> 00:01:56,490
So I'm really excited that
we are entering this region

48
00:01:56,490 --> 00:02:01,320
where we can really investigate
many unexplored territories.

49
00:02:01,320 --> 00:02:04,080
Broad is really the perfect
place for my research group

50
00:02:04,080 --> 00:02:05,340
because I get to interact

51
00:02:05,340 --> 00:02:08,250
with the very best biologists in the world

52
00:02:08,250 --> 00:02:10,020
to really know the most challenging

53
00:02:10,020 --> 00:02:12,420
and pressing questions
so that we can come up

54
00:02:12,420 --> 00:02:15,840
with new ideas in
developing new technologies

55
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:18,210
to help answer these questions.

56
00:02:18,210 --> 00:02:20,250
To me, the point is not to publish

57
00:02:20,250 --> 00:02:21,870
as many papers as possible

58
00:02:21,870 --> 00:02:24,660
but really is to make a bigger impact.

59
